engine

Class Car

  • java.lang.Object
    • engine.Car

  • public class Car
extends java.lang.Object
    Class represents a Car in rush hour puzzle. Car has 4 attributes - ID, LENGTH, ORIENTATION and POSITION of it's head. Head of the car is the most upper left corner of the car.
